statement:
The graph of the function

\[y = f(x) = x(1-x), \quad 0 \leq x \leq 0.5\] is rotated about
\textbf{the y axis} to form a trumpet shape whose base is at (0,0).
Determine the volume of fluid that can be contained inside this shape.

